import { Card, Grid } from "@mui/material";
import SoftBox from "components/SoftBox";
import SoftTypography from "components/SoftTypography";
import MasterCard from "examples/Cards/MasterCard";
import React from "react";
import Header from "layouts/profile/components/Header";
import curved0 from "assets/images/curved-images/curved0.jpg";
import OutlinedCounterCard from "examples/Cards/CounterCards/OutlinedCounterCard";
import Invoice from "layouts/billing/components/Invoice";
import DefaultInfoCard from "examples/Cards/InfoCards/DefaultInfoCard";

const Results = ({decision, contado, cuotas, inflacion, cantidadCuotas }) => {
  return (
    <SoftBox py={3}>
      <Grid container spacing={5} mb={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={7}>
          <SoftBox
            color="white"
            bgColor="dark"
            variant="gradient"
            borderRadius="lg"
            shadow="lg"
            opacity={1}
          >
            <SoftTypography variant="h3" align="center" padding={2} color="white">
              {/* {decision === 'contado'} */}
            </SoftTypography>
          </SoftBox>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} xl={5}>
          <OutlinedCounterCard
            count={23980}
            prefix="$"
            title="Sumatoria de las cuotas ajustadas a valor de hoy"
            pad={0.8}
            color="dark"
            cap={false}
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      <Grid container spacing={5}>
        <Grid item xs={12} xl={4}>
          <Card sx={{ height: "100%" }}>
            <SoftBox
              pt={1}
              px={2}
              display="flex"
              justifyContent="space-between"
              alignItems="center"
            >
              <SoftTypography variant="h5" fontWeight="bold">
                Transaccion
              </SoftTypography>
              {/* <SoftButton variant="outlined" color="info" size="small">
                view all
              </SoftButton> */}
            </SoftBox>
            <SoftBox p={2}>
              <SoftBox component="ul" display="flex" flexDirection="column" p={0} m={0}>
                <Invoice date="Precio de contado" price="$180" />
                <Invoice date="Precio total en cuotas" price="$250" />
                <Invoice date="Inflación mensual estimada" price="$120" />
                <Invoice date="Cantidad de cuotas" price="$180" noGutter />
              </SoftBox>
            </SoftBox>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} xl={4}>
          <MasterCard number={4562112245947852} holder="Leo Messi" expires="11/27" color='dark'  />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6} xl={2}>
          <DefaultInfoCard
            icon="account_balance"
            title="salary"
            description="Belong Interactive"
            value="+$2000"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6} xl={2}>
          <DefaultInfoCard
            icon="paypal"
            title="paypal"
            description="Freelance Payment"
            value="$455.00"
          />
        </Grid>
        {/* <Grid item xs={12}>
          <PaymentMethod />
        </Grid> */}
      </Grid>
    </SoftBox>
  );
};

export default Results;
